text: Iâ€™m always thankful for good QQ noodles and this place usually never disappoints. My favourite chicken feet noodles happen to be just $3.50. Total steal. Chicken rice plus roast pork is also pretty decent. And the side bowl of broth tastes almost like Bak Kut Teh instead of dishwater! I did add a lot of pepper. Polite staff a bonus too.

Price is reasonable.

All staff are friendly.
